des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : customerservice@mirabella.com.au

Mirabella Genio can help you control home appliances nice and easy. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Tuya Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Mirabella Genio" app in android or ios app market;
(2) Register one Genio account in our "Mirabella Genio" app;
(3) You need to have some Mirabella Genio smart devices in hand;
(4) Configure these devices in our "Mirabella Genio" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Mirabella Genio" skill;
(5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7) Search "Mirabella Genio" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of "Mirabella Genio", and you'll be navigated to login page;
(9) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, discover my devices.”
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
”Alexa, set bedroom light to green.“

Currently this skill supports products: smart bulb, smart socket, smart heater....
